{"tid":895314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"超扯警衛！尼泊爾男被疑吸毒竟「被吸」","createTime":"2018-11-09T05:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T06:57:08.000Z","uid":3189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3cd2a2aec77007060bcb20b61daa0ed94a141060","tid":895314,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T05:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181022/640_84716bc320da90c119cf97fc283d3920.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181022%2F640_84716bc320da90c119cf97fc283d3920.jpg&h=a798289d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n28歲男子吉瓦尼山（圖左）被捕，法院判刑20個月。翻攝馬來西亞《中國報》<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞1名尼泊爾籍移工A男，被住宿公寓的警衛懷疑「吸毒」，說要抓他去報警，結果竟是閉門對他施以口交，這名警衛今天被判「違反自然性行為」罪名成立，將要監禁20個月。<br />\n <br />\n根據馬來西亞《中國報》報導，這件事情發生在去年的10月21日，在公寓擔任警衛的單身28歲男子吉瓦尼山，先是叫住了下樓丟垃圾的A男，然後問了A男一堆問題，之後說「懷疑A男吸毒」，要將他送去警局。 <br />\n<br />\n報導中說，之後，吉瓦尼山就藉口說A男必須「先換衣服」，將A男帶到該公寓中的1戶空房內，將A男叫到房間中，脫下A男的褲子，「並吮吸其陽具」。<br />\n<br />\n」，因此宣判監禁20個月，從逮捕日算起，吉瓦尼山是在去年10月22日被捕，因此等於已經服刑12個月，只需再監禁8個月。<br />\n<br />\n（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181022/1452240/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181022%2F1452240%2F&d=yxB5lvmTknxbtXs%2Bbw%2BYuv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=ee5ea319\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181022%2F1452240%2F&h=6c5940e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181022/1452240/</a>"},{"pid":"742f2551f654fb4826f0f55ee55c3cda21812038","tid":895314,"uid":203592,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T06:00:25.000Z","msg":"死gay佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a8c5a2b4129bde4b1aee0a6c57835ffdd1aed0","tid":895314,"uid":61882,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"